{"tid":2319296,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［最強法務部］ 網友收藏大量遊戲音樂影片遭任天堂版權宣告，網友熱議","createTime":"2020-12-10T04:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T06:33:44.000Z","uid":109923,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"31830054e00b5b2bf327f758a7cecac3e5731cfe","tid":2319296,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:09:22.000Z","msg":"一位長年收集統整遊戲音樂的 Youtuber 近日遭到任天堂以宣告版權的方式砍除大量心血，反而受到了許多網友的支持。<br />\n <br />\n這位名為 GilvaSunner 的網友相當喜愛遊戲音樂，在自己成立 10 年的 Youtube 頻道（點此連結）中，收集了許多任天堂老時代的遊戲音樂，不僅分門別類的十分清楚，而且品質也都非常好，某方面來說就是個遊戲音樂博物館。<br />\n <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gilvasunner/status/1161315671839522816?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgilvasunner%2Fstatus%2F1161315671839522816%3Fs%3D21&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpt9AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=bbebd221\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgilvasunner%2Fstatus%2F1161315671839522816%3Fs%3D21&h=6d5feb28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/gilvasunner/status/1161315671839522816?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n不過去年 GilvaSunner 就吃過一次任天堂的版權宣告，當時導致了大量的音樂遭到下架。他在推特上抱怨過這件事，並 PO 出了被 Youtube 系統洗版的警告信。沒想到一年後，類似的惡夢再度重演。<br />\n <br />\n據 GilvaSunner 表示，這次被版權宣告的遊戲包含了《瑪利歐64》、《瑪利歐賽車 Wii》、《薩爾達傳說 時之笛》，而且任天堂還可能要求賠償。<br />\n<br />\n當然，站在法律的角度來說，任天堂的確是有權力做這件事，但是讓很多玩家不能諒解的點是，已經 2020 年了，任天堂卻沒有推出任何數位遊戲音樂，甚至有些遊戲音樂連 CD 都沒有。<br />\n <br />\n也就是說，想聽個遊戲音樂，你可能還得挖出能動的老主機和遊戲，並且玩到那個段落才行。就因為任天堂沒有提供其他任何正版的收聽方式，讓許多玩家感到不滿。<br />\n <br />\n你覺得下手的任天堂合理嗎？歡迎以下面的投票讓我們知道你的想法。"},{"pid":"301597edaa4dfa8ad8374fc8cea949a819193749","tid":2319296,"uid":61954,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:22:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司<br />\n又唔見佢哋告米哈遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f67067009d37a9f2db7c16e9c41c0ed71f5c1e","tid":2319296,"uid":109923,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"301597edaa4dfa8ad8374fc8cea949a819193749","tid":2319296,"uid":61954,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:22:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司<br />\n又唔見佢哋告米哈遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:27:49.000Z","msg":"邊敢告米哈遊，大把game喺中共手上等緊批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正版未入到中國市場，山寨版已經進軍日本賺咗幾億美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共面前，法律含撚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nnintendo 與中國科技公司騰訊合作，於中國推出了符合規格的 nintendo switch主機，更有消息指，中國嚴審任天堂switch，最終只得《New Super Mario Bros. U Deluxe》、《Super Mario Odyssey》、《Mario Kart 8 Deluxe》3隻games能在中國內推出上市。換句話說，即是購買了中國版任天堂主機都只能玩到3隻官方遊戲，而且都是Mario系列！"},{"pid":"14fa7656eb1b27793f8fd19f7be72488b1fa17de","tid":2319296,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T00:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a94b370c7a256128bc66d2c07214574490d8c0","tid":2319296,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:15:01.000Z","msg":"任天堂咁樣claim 版權法等同玩死自己<br />\nSega呢樣就醒好多"},{"pid":"339bfad2b2a42c3b2cfdbc52a66b52bc2ccab334","tid":2319296,"uid":22054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"68a94b370c7a256128bc66d2c07214574490d8c0","tid":2319296,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:15:01.000Z","msg":"任天堂咁樣claim 版權法等同玩死自己<br />\nSega呢樣就醒好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"老任不嬲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09806ae0f5649221ab3b3e47ff856a82136e40d0","tid":2319296,"uid":123869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:23:48.000Z","msg":"任豚：侵犯版權！告得好"},{"pid":"4231f21247222b94fb7960b5959fe93